{"tid":2200404,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"乾/混合性皮膚既你朝早會唔會洗面？","createTime":"2020-09-13T03:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T17:17:13.000Z","uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ae1ed0a562106274fb3ea4fb06101b3256f7aa70","tid":2200404,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:02:56.000Z","msg":"近排睇左好多關於護膚既嘢，發現原來對得電腦多，或者長期暴露於陽光燈光情況搽防曬可以避免皮膚老化同埋生黑色素<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係問題係搽完夜晚要卸妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對於一個男仔黎講絕對係陌生至極，又覺得洗唔洗呀，有d話可以用強力少少既洗面奶代替，但係其實都好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔知會唔會對皮膚唔好，本身皮膚就係敏感肌。<br />\n<br />\n又唔想成日搽咁撚多嘢落塊面度，好驚塊面會依賴左d護膚品長期會搞亂左入面d自然生產，到時可能連油都唔識出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家考慮好唔好朝早起身唔洗面，由得佢一層薄薄既油脂響表面度，或者可能係咁咦濕濕水，再搽面霜，再搽一搽防曬算。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有經驗可以分享"},{"pid":"a7ede64d352283f55833f37397dcead877a1f711","tid":2200404,"uid":251872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"你咩肌"},{"pid":"9cb44b61f14845e1b26e9ab78cdedbf2369863f2","tid":2200404,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7ede64d352283f55833f37397dcead877a1f711","tid":2200404,"uid":251872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"你咩肌"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"應該係乾，又敏感"},{"pid":"de1ce0c93e65eddb137783bbd2ca5bfe53ed9314","tid":2200404,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:17:48.000Z","msg":"過下水就算"},{"pid":"6903cb00ba33af2958105a9b35761b7bf45100ca","tid":2200404,"uid":251872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cb44b61f14845e1b26e9ab78cdedbf2369863f2","tid":2200404,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7ede64d352283f55833f37397dcead877a1f711","tid":2200404,"uid":251872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"你咩肌"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"應該係乾，又敏感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:25:47.000Z","msg":"你應該做好保濕<br />\n早晚至少<br />\n朝早你真係唔想用洗面奶都用水洗下"},{"pid":"52204b37dc58456c404238932d9255b5be8e99d7","tid":2200404,"uid":3093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"你本身早晚點洗面同會搽啲咩落塊面度？<br />\n唔想用卸妝就揀枝化學性防曬<br />\n夜晚用洗面膏就咁就洗得走<br />\n如果你連洗面膏都唔想用就咪鬼搞咁多野"},{"pid":"fc233253292071e676f6ae459188e12d4c916e29","tid":2200404,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52204b37dc58456c404238932d9255b5be8e99d7","tid":2200404,"uid":3093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"你本身早晚點洗面同會搽啲咩落塊面度？<br />\n唔想用卸妝就揀枝化學性防曬<br />\n夜晚用洗面膏就咁就洗得走<br />\n如果你連洗面膏都唔想用就咪鬼搞咁多野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:53:34.000Z","msg":"我一般重點護膚係夜晚，全部都係用dr.G，用洗面奶洗完，抹乾再噴兩嘢補水果支嘢，再黎就係爽膚水，隔陣子再搽保濕乳液，最後可能再搽陣凡士林cream就完。<br />\n<br />\n朝早有時要見人就洗面奶+乳液，放假就無理。"},{"pid":"63f9b7081fa60abe44be18120468b917b80c7994","tid":2200404,"uid":148817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"用factiv <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50fa755a3ea7a49fb866033bc7700f636a2715b","tid":2200404,"uid":148817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"btw 我絲<br />\n朝早唔洗化妝的話只會清水洗面，需要化妝一定會用返洗面奶<br />\n夜晚regular都係用洗面奶"},{"pid":"339bacb75f86333013fc1dc8439a742bac85a17d","tid":2200404,"uid":323845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cb44b61f14845e1b26e9ab78cdedbf2369863f2","tid":2200404,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7ede64d352283f55833f37397dcead877a1f711","tid":2200404,"uid":251872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"你咩肌"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"應該係乾，又敏感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09